snippet.title: Mega-CD Longplay [001] Star Wars: Rebel Assault
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.net

Played By: T-0815

Rebel Assault plays fine on Sega CD (60 fps!). The backround lags are the result of limited Sega CD hardware.
The GFX are far away from the original PC-Version, but the gameplay still works great on the Sega CD!

"Bla bla bla ... there are three TIE Fighter!!! ... They´re firing !!! ... AAAAAAAAAAAAHHHHHH !!!!" I love this part! 19:37  =) -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
